org.safs.tools.input

Class RobotClipboardPasteEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.tools.input.RobotKeyEvent
      • org.safs.tools.input.RobotClipboardPasteEvent

  • public class RobotClipboardPasteEvent
extends RobotKeyEvent
    Derived from RobotKeyEvent for inputting NLS characters. It holds an 'non-standard' string and will copy it to system Clipboard when doEvent called; a group of RobotKeyEvent(Ctrl+v) followed shall paste the content in system Clipboard to focused control.
    Author:
    JunwuMa Sept 22, 2008
    See Also:
    InputKeysParser, Robot, RobotKeyEvent
